    public interface BusRef<TBus extends Bus>
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Adjust Bus'. An BusRef has a reference to a bus object, which will be used for accessing or modifying the bus states.

    The following features are supported:

    • Bus
    See Also:
    NetRefPackage.getBusRef()
